3. 養聲

廣東話：佢係歌手，每日都要養聲，免得聲帶受損。
English: He is a singer and needs to take care of his voice every day to prevent damage to his vocal cords.

4. 票尾

廣東話：我買咗張機票，但係票尾丟咗，成日都冇收據。
English: I bought an airplane ticket, but I lost the receipt part of it, so I don't have a receipt.

5. hacker

廣東話：有hacker黑入我嘅電腦，令到我嘅個人資料都被偷走。
English: A hacker hacked into my computer and stole all my personal information.

6. 石斛蘭

廣東話：我媽媽好鍾意種石斛蘭，佢哋屋企窗台全係石斛蘭。
English: My mom loves to grow stone orchids, and all the windowsills in their home are filled with them.

7. 吊詭

廣東話：佢話佢唔會去，但係又話如果我請佢，佢就會去，真係好吊詭。
English: He said he wouldn't go, but then he said if I invited him, he would go. It's really paradoxical.

8. 吊詭

廣東話：佢話地球係平嘅，真係好吊詭。
English: He said the Earth is flat, which is really absurd.

9. 各為其主

廣東話：佢哋兩個人係各為其主，所以成日都會爭執。
English: Those two people are each working for their own bosses, so they always argue.

10. 軨蓋

廣東話：我地去海邊玩嘅時候，見到好多軨蓋。
English: When we went to the beach, we saw a lot of seashells.

11. 打哥夫

廣東話：佢好鍾意打哥夫，每個禮拜都會去打幾次。
English: He loves to play golf and goes to play a few times every week.

12. 免揀

廣東話：呢間店嘅貨品全部免揀，買咗就要。
English: The goods in this store are all non-refundable, you have to take them once you buy them.

13. 擺闊佬

廣東話：佢最近好喜歡擺闊佬，成日都會買貴嘢。
English: He has been really into showing off his wealth lately and keeps buying expensive things.

14. 廣播劇

廣東話：我尋日聽咗一套好好聽嘅廣播劇。
English: I listened to a really good radio drama yesterday.

15. 錄影機

廣東話：我買咗一部新嘅錄影機，準備拍攝我哋嘅旅行。
English: I bought a new video camera to record our trip.

16. 吟詩吟唔甩

廣東話：佢話佢冇做過，但係證據都指向佢，真係吟詩吟唔甩。
English: He said he didn't do it, but all the evidence points to him. It's really undeniable.

17. 佈道大會

廣東話：我地教會下個禮拜會舉辦佈道大會。
English: Our church will hold an evangelistic meeting next week.

18. 寫手

廣東話：佢係一個寫手，寫咗好多本書。
English: He is a writer and has written many books.

19. 寫手

廣東話：佢係一個代替他人寫作嘅寫手，幫人寫文章、報告等。
English: He is a ghostwriter who writes articles and reports for others.

20. 代打

廣東話：佢係一個職業代打，幫人打遊戲贏比賽。
English: He is a professional substitute who helps people win game competitions.

21. 茶碗

廣東話：我買咗一個日本嘅茶碗，準備用嚟飲茶。
English: I bought a Japanese tea bowl to use for drinking tea.

22. 茶隔

廣東話：我媽媽用茶隔沖茶，令到茶葉同茶湯分開。
English: My mom uses a tea strainer to brew tea, separating the tea leaves from the tea liquid.

23. 只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈

廣東話：佢話我哋唔可以遲到，但係佢自己每日都遲到，真係只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈。
English: He says we can't be late, but he is late every day. It's really a case of "only officials are allowed to set fires, but the common people are not allowed to light lamps."

24. 獨唱

廣東話：佢係一個獨唱歌手，唱歌好好聽。
English: He is a solo singer and sings very beautifully.

25. 快人快事

廣東話：佢係一個快人快事嘅人，做嘢都好爽快。
English: He is a straightforward person who does things very decisively.

26. 四腳獸

廣東話：我哋喺公廁見到四腳獸，好驚人。
English: We saw a four-legged beast in the public restroom, it was quite shocking.

27. 無米粥

廣東話：我哋先煲無米粥，等到條件成熟再談。
English: We are just having a preliminary discussion for now and will talk more when the conditions are right.

28. 義會

廣東話：我哋一班朋友成立一個義會，幫助有需要嘅人。
English: My friends and I started a mutual aid society to help those in need.

29. 榜文

廣東話：政府貼咗一張榜文，通知市民有關嘅消息。
English: The government posted a notice to inform the public of the news.

30. MK名

廣東話：佢網上嘅MK名係「堅系愛音樂」。
English: His MK name on the internet is "Firmly Love Music." [end of text]


